                <ul style="color: var(--text-color);">
                    <li><strong>Bug Fix Sync</strong>: Documented subroutine redefinition fix in controller</li>
                    <li><strong>Infrastructure Update</strong>: Reflected Docker/Redis consolidation and comprehensive infrastructure changes</li>
                    <li><strong>Proxy/K8s Refactoring</strong>: Synchronized documentation with latest Proxy Manager and Kubernetes integration improvements</li>
                    <li><strong>Audit Compliance</strong>: Updated version metadata per DocumentationSyncAudit 2026-01-09</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 12px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
